hopobject.body: I've only just arrived mairie-medis.fr/membres When you're born with star genes, it's no wonder that fame runs in the family ... Christie Brinkley and her daughter Sailor will have you seeing double. The supermodel and her 15-year-old daughter don matching sweaters for Bella Magazine's July 2013 issue. Sailor, Brinkley's daughter with architect Peter Cook, is jumping into the modeling industry and is making her first appearance as a cover girl alongside her star mother. Sailor sports her mother's trademark good looks and long blond locks.
